column7: Trying to bribe me? Hehe. It won't work, but... I won't say no. While we're in such a generous mood, here's a little somethig for you too.
An offering for me, little princeling? Thank you, I love it; and I want you to have a little something of mine.
I'd never say anything less than my most sincere and affectionate opinions of you, Lady Soraka. What do you take me for?
Who's messing with the little prince?
Just leave it to me, little cub!
Don't stray from your path, prince!
Ooh, it would be my pleasure!
I like the sound of that.
Hold on, I have something for you!
I got you something, little prince.
There's something I want you to have.
I don't know why I expected more.
It's not a good idea to make me angry.
You do not want to make me angrier, I'm warning you..
I don't have time for you.
I would never lead you astray~
I would never lead you astray~
I'll claw out your heart next!
Try to deceive me, and I shall destroy you, little prince.
You could have followed me to salvation, but you're just making me angry.
Don't ever refuse my favour like that again, Sett.
